flowchart LR
  LSTM[LSTM 1997<br/>gated recurrent memory]
  QRNN[QRNN 2017<br/>parallel recurrence]
  AFT[AFT 2021<br/>attention-free weighting]
  LinearAttn[Linear Attention 2020<br/>Transformer as RNN]
  Pile[The Pile 2020<br/>open pretraining corpus]
  RWKV[RWKV 2023<br/>WKV state + token shift]
  Raven[RWKV-4 Raven 2023<br/>chat-tuned models]
  Eagle[RWKV-5/6 Eagle Finch 2024<br/>dynamic mix and decay]
  Goose[RWKV-7 Goose 2025<br/>state-first linear LLM]
  Vision[Vision-RWKV 2024<br/>visual sequence modeling]
  Spike[SpikeGPT 2023<br/>spiking recurrent LM]
  Mamba[Mamba 2023<br/>selective SSM competitor]
  Misread[Common misread<br/>not just an old RNN]

  LSTM --> QRNN --> RWKV
  AFT --> RWKV
  LinearAttn --> RWKV
  Pile --> RWKV
  RWKV --> Raven --> Eagle --> Goose
  RWKV --> Vision
  RWKV --> Spike
  RWKV -.baseline and rival in linear revival.-> Mamba
  RWKV -.warns against.-> Misread

